{"tid":2299563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又又又中國製］安心出行個app要攞你手機一大堆權限","createTime":"2020-11-25T01:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T03:35:51.000Z","uid":216800,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4947c997270a339c80f56d3e690d9d86cfbd4d13","tid":2299563,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXRLSyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXRLSyU.jpg&h=6b2043df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WO8is7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWO8is7e.jpg&h=7b1c4403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AA675TV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAA675TV.jpg&h=217b844d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECeJEdW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECeJEdW.jpg&h=320a6cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講唔裝政府個咩 app 「安心上路」？「安心出殯」？「安心出軌」(許志安推介?)？、「安心中出」？🤷 <br />\n唔嘟，遲吓就以後冇得飲茶 🚫 ☕、冇得搭車 🚫🚕，甚至唔嘟就响樓下管理處冇得返上屋企 🚷，呢次我父母大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n請問呢款機 iNo CP09，可以點裝？<br />\n<br />\n裝咗的話，聽講政府一知道你去過邊啲地方，就會隨時📲打比你，通知你一家好危險，要立刻起行入去隔離營 🔐。<br />\n<br />\n但我唔係好明，個咩app呢，攞你部機以下呢啲權限，係要嚟做乜㗎？⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\n<br />\n📷Device &amp; app history<br />\n* retrieve running apps <br />\n（點解要睇吓我部機運行緊其他嘅app?）<br />\n<br />\n📷Photos/Media/Files<br />\n* read the contents of your USB storage <br />\n（點解要睇吓我電話有乜嘢檔案?）<br />\n* modify or delete the contents of your USB storage <br />\n（點解要幫我删除我電話啲檔案?）<br />\n<br />\n📷Camera<br />\n* take pictures and videos <br />\n（係咪可以响我唔知情下，幫我開鏡頭拍片？）<br />\n<br />\n📷Wi-Fi connection information<br />\n* view Wi-Fi connections<br />\n（點解要知我駁住乜嘢 WiFi ? 同附近有乜 WiFi ？）<br />\n<br />\n📷 Other<br />\n* receive data from Internet<br />\n（我每個月冇乜data用喎，係咪政府幫我比錢交電話月費？）<br />\n* view network connections <br />\n（點解要睇我部機用緊3G，4G定5G，定WiFi？點解要知我有冇用緊VPN？）<br />\n* allow Wi-Fi Multicast reception <br />\n（點解政府要親切地幫我發multicast packet 比附近智慧燈柱咁叻嘅？）<br />\n* run at startup<br />\n（一開機就自己在背景啟動，驚我唔記得開app，真係好親切呀！）<br />\n* prevent device from sleeping<br />\n（唔比部機進入休眠狀態，咁會唔會好食電㗎？）<br />\n<br />\n呢個app最有趣嘅地方，係佢叫你周圍嘟，紀錄低你每日24小時去過邊，但你自己响個app度，原來係睇唔返自己去過邊嘅紀錄㗎 ！咁政府又話，佢唔會偷你部機的紀錄。咁我想問，咁到底嘟完啲紀錄，係咪其實比👻睇？"},{"pid":"1dea01153872564c8df3bb0660ec8cc260c59f7e","tid":2299563,"uid":317019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:34:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25542caa6168bfaa3bd06623567bb1e63ac5eb46","tid":2299563,"uid":325636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ef3e7241e8379a81ecd63fbf0ee5952124f483","tid":2299563,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"香港IT係咪死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e148d561fa2cdb7f9cdc02ea408408cd3fb10b","tid":2299563,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"送哂啲資料俾大陸仲點安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8039f73f146a873be71f0c50a9714f5ed8f13de6","tid":2299563,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:48:01.000Z","msg":"推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3f617cf0f8f2e4420178f23d4c830e2eda2fad","tid":2299563,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"我買部新電話 太空卡得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebd45660a1542d0b1bc8d2fcfe2ed34b8cbec51","tid":2299563,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb3f617cf0f8f2e44